Teaching English in Yogyakarta, Indonesia: Jobs & Certification
Official Blog of American TESOL Institute
On April 23, 2014,
in ,
by tesol
For those seeking an artsy cultural city look no further than . This city is the capital of the Java island, and full of all things art. Teaching jobs are plentiful, and you should be able to find one that will take care of your $800 monthly living costs.
Once you settle in make sure to explore the exceptional batik art, local ballet, and world-renowned puppet shows. Aggy loves this city, and has a long list of why you will too on her .
